{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the mouse (or gamepad) to control your character and jump as high as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some rocks are very slippery, so take your time! Grab onto them with your hammer and carefully plan your next move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/GIF_1.gif?t=1739803282\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Climb mountains and challenging levels with your trusty hammer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you fall, you lose all your progress, a true test of patience and skill!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game automatically saves your progress, allowing you to pick up exactly where you left off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compare your best times with other players through the integrated global leaderboard!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can\u2019t die, but every misstep serves as a reminder of your determination... or frustration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A tribute to human resilience, where every fall is a new opportunity (or perhaps a reason to throw your controller across the room).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/GIF_2.gif?t=1739803282\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customization</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock unique skins and customizations for your cardboard box and character by completing challenges and levels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541550/extras/customization.gif?t=1739803282\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Notes</h2><ul cla